  "prompt": "What is the average salary of IT professional having 10 years experience in India?",
  "response": "The average salary of an IT professional with 10 years of experience in India can vary significantly based on several factors such as the specific field within IT (software development, cybersecurity, data science, etc.), the company, geographic location, and the individual's skill set.\n\nAs of 2023, an IT professional with 10 years of experience in India typically earns somewhere between \u20b915 lakhs to \u20b930 lakhs per annum. High-demand skills or roles at top-tier companies, such as those in fintech, AI, or cloud computing, might push salaries even higher, potentially reaching \u20b940 lakhs or more.\n\nFor the most accurate and current salary data, it is advisable to refer to industry reports, salary surveys, and job portals such as Naukri, Glassdoor, or LinkedIn.",
